<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink347">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>yeḻiṟṟakai yiḷamulai poliyap</l>
<l>porippūm puṉkiṉ muṟitimir poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,  </l>
<l>when leaves of the Puṉku tree whose flowers are like puffed rice  </l>
<l>are [turned into paste] and smeared to make young beautiful breasts glitter. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
